snippet.title: Unedited: Amber Portwood's Christmas Eve Argument with Andrew Glennon
snippet.description:
A Fully unedited version of the argument that occurred between Andrew Glennon and Amber Portwood. Please note - the audio may be difficult to hear.

If you or a friend need help leaving a DV relationship - please know help is available 24/7 at the National DV Hotline

Call 1-800-799-7233.

Amber Portwood is still employed by MTV despite her arrest. Please contact MTV and Viacom to express your concerns.

Twitter @MTV @Viacom
